               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Gadla Qirqos “Vita of Cyricus” (fols. 3ra-98vb) &#xD;
II) Taʾāmra Qirqos “Miracles of Cyricus” (fols. 99ra-130rb): 33 miracles.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                     
                     <incipit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </incipit>
                     <explicit>
                        <foreign xml:lang="en"/>
                     </explicit>
                     <note/>
                  </msItem>
                  <!--The data in the items below refers to other items. please remove this items and move the information to the appropriate place.-->
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                     <note>- Text I is divided into sections to be read each month, the same as in<ref type="mss" corresp="ESamq007">AMQ-007</ref>.</note>
                     <note>- In Text II, all the 33 miracles are numbered. The numeral 27 is repeted twice and the following numeration continues wrongly, so that the last numeral is 32 instead of 33.</note>
                     <note>The miracles are the same and in the same sequence as<ref type="mss" corresp="ESamq007">AMQ-007</ref>.</note>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
